## Pasos de Implementación Detallados

### Paso 1: Crear Migración SQL para Actualizar Cliente OIDC

**Archivo:** `provider/migrations/016_add_offline_access_to_writehub_client.sql`

```sql
-- Migration 016: Add offline_access scope and refresh_token grant type to WriteHub Client
-- This migration updates the WriteHub OIDC client to support offline_access scope
-- and refresh_token grant type for automatic token renewal

-- Update WriteHub client to include refresh_token grant type and offline_access scope
UPDATE oidc_clients
SET 
    grant_types = ARRAY['authorization_code', 'refresh_token'],
    allowed_scopes = ARRAY['openid', 'email', 'profile', 'offline_access'],
    updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
WHERE client_id = 'writehub-client';

-- Verify the update
DO $$
DECLARE
    updated_grant_types TEXT[];
    updated_allowed_scopes TEXT[];
BEGIN
    SELECT grant_types, allowed_scopes
    INTO updated_grant_types, updated_allowed_scopes
    FROM oidc_clients
    WHERE client_id = 'writehub-client';
    
    -- Verify refresh_token is in grant_types
    IF NOT ('refresh_token' = ANY(updated_grant_types)) THEN
        RAISE EXCEPTION 'refresh_token not found in grant_types';
    END IF;
    
    -- Verify offline_access is in allowed_scopes
    IF NOT ('offline_access' = ANY(updated_allowed_scopes)) THEN
        RAISE EXCEPTION 'offline_access not found in allowed_scopes';
    END IF;
    
    RAISE NOTICE '✅ WriteHub client updated successfully';
    RAISE NOTICE '   Grant types: %', array_to_string(updated_grant_types, ', ');
    RAISE NOTICE '   Allowed scopes: %', array_to_string(updated_allowed_scopes, ', ');
END $$;
```

**Verificación Post-Migración:**

```sql
-- Verificar que la migración se aplicó correctamente
SELECT 
    client_id,
    grant_types,
    allowed_scopes,
    refresh_token_lifetime,
    updated_at
FROM oidc_clients
WHERE client_id = 'writehub-client';

-- Resultado esperado:
-- grant_types: {authorization_code,refresh_token}
-- allowed_scopes: {openid,email,profile,offline_access}
```

